  "prompt": "What are some good movies about a person that has a hidden power that he/she couldn't use until put into a pressure situation?",
  "response": "Here are some movies featuring characters who discover or unleash hidden powers under pressure:\n\n1. **\"Spider-Man\" (2002)** - Peter Parker, a seemingly ordinary teenager, discovers his superhuman abilities after being bitten by a radioactive spider. His powers manifest more fully when he has to confront dangerous situations threatening those he loves.\n\n2. **\"Limitless\" (2011)** - Eddie Morra, a struggling writer, takes a mysterious pill that unlocks the full potential of his brain, enhancing his cognitive abilities dramatically. His newfound talents emerge primarily when he's faced with high stakes.\n\n3. **\"Unbreakable\" (2000)** - David Dunn discovers his superhuman strength and resilience after surviving a horrific train wreck without a scratch. His potential unfolds gradually, especially when faced with the truth about his unique abilities.\n\n4. **\"The Matrix\" (1999)** - Neo, an ordinary computer hacker, discovers his true potential in a simulated reality where he has extraordinary abilities. His powers are unlocked during intense confrontations with agents and others in the Matrix.\n\n5. **\"The Bourne Identity\" (2002)** - Jason Bourne, suffering from amnesia, gradually uncovers his exceptional skills in hand-to-hand combat and strategic thinking as he's pursued by assassins, revealing his true capabilities under pressure.\n\n6. **\"Shazam!\" (2019)** - A young boy named Billy Batson can transform into an adult superhero by uttering the word \"Shazam.\" His powers come to light when he faces life-threatening situations and learns to embrace his newfound abilities.\n\n7. **\"Lucy\" (2014)** - Lucy, a woman who gains access to increased brain capacity after being exposed to a synthetic drug, starts to demonstrate extraordinary powers as she pushes through dire circumstances.\n\n8. **\"Chronicle\" (2012)** - Three high school friends gain telekinetic abilities after discovering a mysterious object. Their powers develop and escalate when put in stressful situations, leading to both personal and destructive consequences.\n\n9. **\"The Last Airbender\" (2010)** - Aang, the last Airbender, initially struggles with his powers, but as he faces adversaries and threats, he learns to harness and control them effectively.\n\n10. **\"The Secret\" (2006)** - In this documentary, while not a traditional film, it showcases how hidden powers (the law of attraction, in this case) can be realized when individuals are in challenging situations, prompting them to change their mindset and approach to life.\n\nThese films explore themes of self-discovery, overcoming fear, and personal growth in the face of adversity.",
